Text:
ATK doesn't always move a model's sets to Archives, even if they're old.  No idea what their reasoning is. 

Very pretty face.  I'd love to see how she looks today at 32.

Yeah, I just noticed that the photos of Jazz from 2000 are in Archives, but her pics from 2004 are still in Exotics.  I'll guess as long as sets are downloaded enough, then they can avoid being dumped into the Archives.

At age 32, she's probably moved on with her life and is now a young mother.  And is wondering how to keep her kids from finding out about these wild oats she sowed in her youth.
BTW, I thought your new nim was "FinalAeon".
Heh... no I don't have a new name.
